<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV17">
<l>ēkamūrtti mūṉṟumūrtti nālumūrtti naṉmaicēr</l>
<l>pōkamūrtti puṇṇiyattiṉ mūrttiyeṇṇil mūrttiyāy</l>
<l>nākamūrtti cayaṉamāyna laṅkaṭaṟki ṭantumē</l>
<l>lākamūrtti yāyavaṇṇa meṉkolāti tēvaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O primordial God! You recline on the good ocean with the body of the snake</l>
<l rend="indent">as [Your] bed.</l>
<l>Furthermore, of what nature is Your being with a bodied form,</l>
<l>Being with countless benevolent forms, one form, three forms, four forms,</l>
<l>An enjoyable form, the [very] form of merits?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
